    <cinematic type="dialog" line="" duration="2" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Doing what I do, you see a lot of things." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Shit that'll make your everyday S&amp;M'r look like a kindergarten teacher." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Soldiers raping soldiers," />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="coked-up gang bangers," />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="senior citizen acid-trips, " />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="bestiality on a bed of nails," />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="climax at 220 volts!" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="But love?" duration = "3"/>
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Jesus." />
    <cinematic type="camera" duration="0" posX="726" posY="152" posZ="843.5" targetX="725" targetY="152" targetZ="842"  />
    <cinematic type="camera" duration="80000" posX="728" posY="152" posZ="845" targetX="725" targetY="152" targetZ="842"  />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="We're not talking Montagues and Capulets here." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="No, no, no, it's Angels and Demons and Humans!" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="There's an order of things, and as far as they're concerned, we're scraping the bottom of the barrel." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="That doesn't keep 'em from slummin', the best of 'em coming down for a piece of homo sapien ass." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="It makes you wonder... who's seducing who?" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Sure, transdimensional copulation is gonna ensue, but Mommy, Daddy, Baby, and a picket fence?" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="No sir! Access denied! Get out of town! It's not happening!" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="And from the looks of things, with a fuckin' Jinn, no less!" />
    <cinematic type="camera" duration="0" posX="719" posY="152.3" posZ="842.7"  targetX="726.3" targetY="152.3" targetZ="843.1"/>
    <cinematic type="camera" duration="100000" posX="714.4" posY="152.3" posZ="844.17" targetX="726.3" targetY="152.3" targetZ="843.1" />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="That's all I can tell you about the demon, but your girl..." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Rose Doherty, born and raised in Ireland, relocated to London on her 18th birthday," />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="then one day... poof! She disappears, never to be seen again." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="You and I know the rest of the story..." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="She moves to China to shack up with her demon boyfriend out of sight, but not hidden well enough," />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="because the locals bring out their pitchforks and burn the place down, extra-crispy lovers inside." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Case closed and shut, except for one thing..." />
    <cinematic type="camera" duration="0" posX="726" posY="152" posZ="843.5" targetX="725" targetY="152" targetZ="842"  />
    <cinematic type="camera" duration="80000" posX="725" posY="152" posZ="842" targetX="725" targetY="152" targetZ="842"  />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="It's total bullshit. I can smell it." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="I've been doing this a long time, and I can see the signs a mile away." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="That being said... tell your mistress this is where I get off." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="This one's too hot, even for me." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="An audience of one wins no Pulitzers." />
    <cinematic type="dialog" line="Oh, and your girl? She's in the book. Look her up." />
